hbl.jag.tri.lib

Class BNA2VERDAT

  • java.lang.Object
    • hbl.jag.tri.lib.BNA2VERDAT

  • public class BNA2VERDAT
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a utility class that reads in a BNA file of map segments in its constructor and provides a method for outputting a verdat file in the standard GNOME format. A BNA2VERDAT class has a input (String with the absolute address of the BNA map to be used as input)
    Author:
    jag
